Gate (Erc20 DAI Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard DAI "Dai")
Gate (Erc20 REP Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard REP "Augur")
Gate (Erc20 USDC Address) (Erc20 Deploy Standard USDC "USD Coin" 6)

-- Now deploy our cTokens
Gate (SLToken slZRX Address) (SLToken Deploy CErc20 slZRX "Test 0x ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 ZRX Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (SLToken slBAT Address) (SLToken Deploy CErc20 slBAT "Test Basic Attention Token ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 BAT Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (SLToken slDAI Address) (SLToken Deploy CErc20 slDAI "Test Dai ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 DAI Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (SLToken slREP Address) (SLToken Deploy CErc20 slREP "Test Augur ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 REP Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (SLToken slETH Address) (SLToken Deploy CEther slETH "Test Ether ðŸ“ˆ" (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 0.2e9 8)
Gate (SLToken slUSDC Address) (SLToken Deploy CErc20 slUSDC "Test USD Coin ðŸ“ˆ" (Erc20 USDC Address) (Comptroller Address) (InterestRateModel InterestRateModel Address) 2e-4 8)

